Author

OVERVIEW 

- The challenge

  Users should be able to:
    - View a clean, styled list of tasks
    - Add new tasks to the list
    - Edit existing tasks
    - Delete tasks using a checkbox
    - Persist data in a PostgreSQL database
    - Experience a smooth UI with immediate feedback

- Links
    - GitHub: https://github.com/Argoneo

- My process
  - Built with
    - HTML
    - CSS3
    - JavaScript (ES6)
    - Node.js
    - Express.js
    - EJS templating
    - PostgreSQL
    - dotenv (for environment variable management)
    - MVC pattern and RESTful routes
    - Fully responsive UI

- What I learned
  - How to set up a Node.js and Express server
  - How to integrate PostgreSQL with Express using pg
  - How to use EJS to render dynamic views
  - How to structure a RESTful CRUD application
  - How to manage form submissions and user input
  - How to hide and manage environment variables using dotenv
  - How to handle real-time interaction with forms using JavaScript

